title: Unlimited high quality photos storage for Pixel 4a
content:
Will the Google Pixel 4a device retain its free Unlimited High Quality Pictures/Videos cloud storage after 1st of June 2021 on Google photos?

I just started using Google photos after purchasing a Google Pixel 4a and I found myself really liking the service. Now that I got the news about Google photos new rules, I am a bit worried and need some closure. Thank you!
